se.soprasteria.automatedtesting.webdriver.api.utility

Class Credentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.soprasteria.automatedtesting.webdriver.api.utility.Credentials

  • public class Credentials
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages credentials for a user and provides an interface for either creating users yourself or extracting them from the XML. Please refer to the users.xml file in the resource folder of the reference implementation to see how to provide users to the system.

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      Credentials()
      Initialize a user with dummy values (id:dummy, user:badUsername, pw:badPassword, pin:9876) and provide an interface to the XML file with users.
      Credentials(java.lang.String UserID)
      Initialize a user based on userid and XML file.
